column3: description

The K200 model by Sanjo is one of our iconic designs, boasting over 90 years of history. It has been reinvented to celebrate the original while preserving some of its key features: a canvas upper and a stitched logo on the side. To make this model even more special, we've revolutionized it with modern details and higher-quality materials: a textile tag on the tongue, full inner lining, cushioned insole, coated eyelets, and a TPR outsole offering excellent durability, abrasion resistance, and lightweight properties. Made in Portugal COMPOSITION Upper: 100% Organic Cotton Canvas, resistant to sunlight. Sole: 100% Vegan TPR Insole: Memory foam Lining: Mesh VEGAN INESCOPEnsures the main chemical nature of the material does not include fibers of animal origin (such as hides, leather, silk, wool, or down). CARBON FOOTPRINTAdherence to a carbon footprint reduction plan, with specific actions to lower IEC emissions released into the atmosphere during manufacturing. GLOBAL ORGANIC TEXTILE STANDARDWith the GOTS certification, we ensure compliance with social, environmental, health, and safety standards. We prioritize workplace safety and value certified fabrics across all our markets.

Having more durable sneakers means they might get a little dirty. But that doesn't mean they'll get scratched or torn. This edition of Sanjo sneakers, featuring a Cordura upper, is designed to offer long-lasting performance and resistance to abrasion, cuts, and tears. Its water-resistant property ensures your feet stay dry. Made in Portugal COMPOSITION Upper: Cordura Lining: Mesh Sole: 100% Vegan TPR

Stay warm and dry on cold and rainy days with Sanjo made from Burel, a water-resistant fabric crafted from 100% natural wool. Born in the heart of Serra da Estrela, Burel has been traditionally used by high-mountain shepherds. Durable and versatile, it transitioned from cloaks and coats for rainy, snowy, and cold mountain days to becoming an essential part of Sanjo's construction. Made in Portugal COMPOSITION Upper: Burel – water-resistant, easy to maintain, eco-friendly, 100% Portuguese Lining: Mesh Sole: 100% Vegan TPR

The K100 model by Sanjo is one of our iconic designs, boasting over 90 years of history. It has been reinvented to celebrate the original while preserving some of its key features: a canvas upper and a stitched logo on the side. To make this model even more special, we've revolutionized it with modern details and higher-quality materials: a textile tag on the tongue, full inner lining, cushioned insole, coated eyelets, and a TPR outsole offering excellent durability, abrasion resistance, and lightweight properties.
